metadata.name: Krampus
metadata.description:
"The only Web3 Companion you will ever need"  

To claim a demon you will need to burn a fəmilyərz.     

**What is a fəmilyərz?**   
360 web3 companions   
They are a web3 companion which can help you to identify other Occult & Dark Arts lovers amongst a sea of Anons.   
They are stage 1 of a 2 stage process.   

The utility is the community we build & the fəmilyər who will forever be by your side +   

*Have a fəmilyərz set as a PFP on the full moon & receive a monthly airdrop in sequence!*  

**Join the Discord for all information!**
